# Change log

## [unreleased]

## [0.4.0] - 2015-07-21
### Changed
- Implemented dynamic width on panels.

## [0.3.0] - 2015-07-15
### Added
- Background support in app, always looking at the focus panel. The transition needs work there...

## [0.2.0] - 2015-07-13
### Added
- Animation and centre panels.

### Changed
- Upgraded to `react@0.14.0-beta1`.

### Changed

## [0.1.0] - 2015-06-29
### Added
- `Panels`, `PanelContainer` and `Panel` components.
- `createPanelsRuntime` makes a new runtime taking initial data returning an `App` component and a
  `redux` instance.
- Playground with dummy data.
- Tests scaffold.
